-image-340493\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/elbe.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Elbe Blake is a WordPress marketing theme designed for marketing consultants, freelancers, or small agencies. This Genesis child theme has seven color options, lots of features, and it is SEO friendly.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://www.web-savvy-marketing.com/store/elbe-blake/\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Elbe Blake theme</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Identity theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/identity-multionepage-business-wordpress-theme/9101950\"><img src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/identity.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Identity is a Multi/One Page WordPress Theme that can fit creative design agency, web development agency, start-up company or any business company.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/identity-multionepage-business-wordpress-theme/9101950\">Purchase Identity theme</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Elision theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/elision-retina-multipurpose-wordpress-theme/6382990\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/elision.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>ELISION is a retina multi-purpose WordPress theme.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/elision-retina-multipurpose-wordpress-theme/6382990\">Purchase Elision theme</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Evoke theme</h2>\n<p style=