der to expedite the process we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a title=\"Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins\" href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/\">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin <strong>Multilingual Ready</strong>.</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">LVY theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://demo.flothemes.com/?theme=lvy\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/lvy.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Lovely is customizable and minimalistic WordPress theme suitable for for photographers.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://demo.flothemes.com/?theme=lvy\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase LVY theme</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Custom Post Widget</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/custom-post-widget/\"><img src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/cpw.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>This plugin enables you to edit and display Content Blocks in a sidebar widget or using a shortcode.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/custom-post-widget/\">Download Custom Post Widget</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">EU Cookie Law</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/eu-cookie-law/\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/eu.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>EU Cookie Law informs users that your site uses cookies, with option to lock scripts before consent. Light + Customizable style.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/eu-cookie-law/\">Download EU Cookie Law</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=KXCkxFuIngc:rXxYzZwx64Q:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=KXCkxFuIngc:rXxYzZwx64Q:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=KXCkxFuIngc:rXxYzZwx64Q:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=KXCkxFuIngc:rXxYzZwx64Q:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=KXCkxFuIngc:rXxYzZwx64Q:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=KXCkxFuIngc:rXxYzZwx64Q:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/KXCkxFuIngc\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:88:\"https://wpml.org/2015/08/this-week-compatible-lvy-custom-post-widget-eu-cookie-law/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:83:\"https://wpml.org/2015/08/this-week-compatible-lvy-custom-post-widget-eu-cookie-law/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s: